"Hi, I'm Sister Jesus Christ! I'm a new nun sent by...uh... the nun king to start...nunning here."

The Sexton spits on the ground. "First time I heard of it. Sounds like a fishy story to me. But that don't matter, I ain't heard nothin' from the Mother superior, so til she says you go in, I ain't openin' these doors."
> possess sexton

