Whoa...

That feels WAY different.  The world is bleary and shifting as you stare out through eyes wracked with cataracts. You blink in surprise, looking down at your suddenly wrinkled, be-liver spotted hands. You are now inhabiting the Sexton's body.

You feel a weight in your pocket and, when you reach in, you pull out a large set of iron keys. These look like they might come in useful!

