"Oh! Mr.Twinzell! No, of course not, none but the one they've got hidden away. Of course, I haven't actually seen it myself. I'm not privy to the secret room where they've got it hid. The Mother Superior was very careful to make sure that the passage was completely hidden from sight. I think you'd have to have the most finely developed senses in the world to find it!"
