"Wha? How did you know..."

"Did you find out any more delightful gossip since last we spoke?" says Sister Ursula, giggling like a schoolgirl. "I remember you said that you thought you'd figured out who our dear Sister Heloise's secret beau is! I am just so excited to hear the latest scuttlebutt!"

"Er...did I? I'm afraid I don't know anything about that," you say hesitantly.  Hmm, you certainly don't know anything about that.  But Sister Grizelda might! If only you could actually access her memories! Failing that, you'll just have to get her to talk somehow.
