> speak to Grizelda

> speak to Grizelda
"So I hear you know some gossip about Sister Heloise?" you say in what you hope in a nonchalant tone of voice.

"Oh, sister, do I!" cries Sister Grizelda, apparently always eager to gossip. "Now I couldn't get a name...but you know how Sister Heloise just dotes on the church cat? Why, she seems to be the only person that nasty cat will allow to pet her! I know for a fact that Heloise would NEVER be with anyone that cat didn't also accept."

"So it must be whoever else that cat lets pet him?" you say.

"Exactly!"

Well. At least that'll help you narrow down the field.
