A large scepter, shaped like a shepherd's crook and covered with tiny crabbed inscriptions in an unfamiliar language.
> x plaque

> x plaque
"Ceremonial scepter recovered from the ruins of the Forbidden City of Jazzarrdo on the Island of Roach, Macronesia archipeligo. Circa 1600 ? Consecreted to Great Schlubb of the Multitudinous Eyes, one of the unknowable deities of the deep."

Huh. That seems an oddly... heathen artifact to store here in a convent.
> speak to mother

> speak to mother
"Well, well, well, Mr. Farkis!" purrs the Mother Superior, flashing bedroom eyes at you. "To what do I owe this unexpected pleasure?"

She leans across the desk, licking her lips hungrily, and looks at you expectantly.
