> use boat

> use boat
"C'mon, Mom!" you say happily as you jump into the boat. "Let's get out of here!"

Mom hugs you close. "Oh Ilemauzer, honey, I don't think I've ever heard a better idea! Give me a hand with these oars!"

You give your mother a toothy smile.  It's good to see her again.  Aunty Grimalkin is going to absolutely faint when she realizes that you survived the Basilica de Sangre... and you came back with your mom too!

You paddle away, glad to forever leave behind the Basilica de Sangre.

